                     <interp inst="t18320105-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="mail"></interp>
               he, being a person employed by and under the Post-office of Great Britain, in certain business relating to the said office (i.e.) in <rs id="t18320105-1-deflabel2" type="occupation">sorting certain letters</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320105-1-defend104 t18320105-1-deflabel2"></join>, to wit, franked and paid, brought to the <placeName id="t18320105-1-crimeloc3">General Post-office, at the parish of St. Anne and Agnes, in London</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-1-crimeloc3" type="placeName" value="General Post-office, at the parish of St. Anne and Agnes, in London"></interp>
