                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320105-1-off1 t18320105-1-crimeloc3"></join>, on the <rs id="t18320105-1-cd4" type="crimeDate">22nd of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320105-1-off1 t18320105-1-cd4"></join>, at the said parish, a certain letter then lately before brought to the said office, to be sent by the post, for and to be delivered to a certain person at Axminster, in Devon, to wit, the <rs id="t18320105-1-viclabel5" type="occupation">Rev</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320105-1-victim107 t18320105-1-viclabel5"></join>. 
