                        Edward 
                        James Todd
                     <interp inst="t18320105-1-person105" type="surname" value="James Todd"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18320105-1-person105" type="given" value="Edward"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18320105-1-person105" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , and containing a Bank post-bill for 10l., came into his hands and possession whilst so employed, as aforesaid, and that he then and there being so employed, feloniously did secrete and embezzle the said letter, containing the said Bank post-bill, the said bill being then in force, and the property of the said 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320105-1-victim107" type="victimName">
                           Edward James 
