                  </rs>; against the Statute.</p>
               <p>2nd COUNT, that he did feloniously steal and take out of the said letter, whilst employed as aforesaid, the said 10l. Bank post-bill, the property of the said Edward James Todd.</p>
               <p>3rd and 4th COUNTS, the same, only stating the Bank post-bill to be the property of 
               
